majordomo (0.1.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release. Read and report Google Chat task activity: tasks by
    assignee, space, and date; spaces, people, messages, and threads. A cache
    fast path with a live Chat-API fallback, a privacy sieve, and an optional
    MCP front door.

